title: Seoul National University Vegan Buffet
description: All-you-can-eat lunch buffet at Seoul National University open to the public. Directions: Get off at Seoul National University station exit 3, take bus 5513 to 법대입구 (law department stop), walk up the small hill from bus stop, and the cafe is there.
streetAddress: 1 Gwanak-ro, Gwanak-gu, Seoul, Asian Research Institute, Building 101
